_sText:
This is actually my first map but I've been working on it for so long that I think it's release worthy.
Installation: put the .BSP in C:\Programfiles\Steam\steamapps\your username\counterstrike: source\maps
Removal: just delete the .bsp
Don't completely judge it by the screen shots, If you have the time to test it please do.

And please leave constructive feedback.

Enjoy!
